      "span_text": "To test whether generic language might have direct selective effects in the case of social groups, Marjorie Rhodes, Christina Tworek and I created a picture book that depicted a group of imaginary peoplethe Zarpies-who were diverse for race, ethnicity, gender, and age; the group thus could not be mapped on to any familiar, essentialized social group [CITATION_1] .",
